  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "President of Cuba-- his name was President Bru had set a deadline for the presentation of the demanded funds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this gentleman from New York had the funds with him, but he thought he could perhaps argue him down a bit per capita.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the president wasn't having any, and while several days passed, and he declared that the time limit had elapsed, and there was no further conversation about this matter, and the ship was to leave.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Meanwhile, there was correspondence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody suggested that the come and bring us to an island off the coast of New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were all kinds of negotiations going on with New York with other countries in the hemisphere, specifically the Dominican Republic.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And meanwhile, the captain needed at least 24 hours to load provisions, because obviously we had been under way for close to two weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were in the harbor for a week, and now we were supposed to leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he did-- he did go to get the permission from the Cubans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He went on land himself to load provisions for another 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Secret Service got after them, and they were expelled through the efforts of, I think, Mr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hoover-- well, at least through the Secret Service-- and they escaped to Havana.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Havana was a breeding ground for all kinds of distasteful political activities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so this agent was dispatched by way of the ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans had in mind, first of all, the Jews will pay for the trip.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Secondly, this was kind of a test run to see what the world's reaction would be to whatever outcome this particular trip would have.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
